Repository Name Unauthorized: Our Lady of the Lake University Archives
Notes:
Prominent record series held include: •        Records from Administrative Units and Schools and Departments: Records of Board of Trustees, President's Office, Vice-Presidents' Offices, Provost’s Office, Alumni Office, Faculty Assembly, Councils and Committees.
•        Personal papers of Gibson, Guadalupe (Social Work) 1917-2000; Weniger, Delbert (Biology) 1960-1990; Woods, Sr. Frances Jerome (Sociology) 1922-1992.
•        Scrapbooks, Postcards, memorabilia, and regalia.
•        Published resources written by and about OLL leaders.
